// Pillars.astro — "Why Build It" vision section with four pillars
---

<section class="section" id="vision">
  <p class="section-label">Why Build It</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">More than a <em>sport.</em><br>A club worth forming.</h2>
  <p class="section-body">
    Rugby has a culture unlike anything else in sport — forged through hard
    training, honest competition, respect for opponents, and fellowship after
    the final whistle. The aim is to bring that tradition to Spotsylvania in a
    way that forms character, welcomes families, and gives local players a badge
    to earn.
  </p>

  <div class="pillars">
    <div class="pillar">
      <div class="pillar-num">01</div>
      <div class="pillar-title">All Levels Welcome</div>
      <p>No experience necessary. Rugby rewards courage, effort, and teachability as much as skill. We want to hear from anyone willing to learn the game properly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar">
      <div class="pillar-num">02</div>
      <div class="pillar-title">Real Fellowship</div>
      <p>The fellowship after the match is part of the game. What begins on the pitch — trust, grit, and shared effort — can become friendship that lasts for decades.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar">
      <div class="pillar-num">03</div>
      <div class="pillar-title">A Club for Life</div>
      <p>From first practice to coaching the next generation, a good rugby club grows with its members. The goal is something permanent, not a flash in the pan.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar">
      <div class="pillar-num">04</div>
      <div class="pillar-title">Rooted Locally</div>
      <p>This club should belong to this community. We may compete regionally, but our identity should be shaped by the people and place we call home.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
